edBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T02:36:26.000Z","msg":"呢條路個Idea Loop左幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3214cb70274e793faba3876d5e409913a3c49b71","tid":530581,"uid":115525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"210ea137164d82edeacad8c0547a7eebc50fca45","tid":530581,"uid":77196,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T02:36:26.000Z","msg":"呢條路個Idea Loop左幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T02:38:30.000Z","msg":"我都想知聽左幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92b108105dbe68125ddf58b6f75ec346baaf766","tid":530581,"uid":40428,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T02:39:48.000Z","msg":"老死個陣都未必撥到款<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f8f4e053b0060b61232fe7d934fb39f08e7d64","tid":530581,"uid":8717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f92b108105dbe68125ddf58b6f75ec346baaf766","tid":530581,"uid":40428,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T02:39:48.000Z","msg":"老死個陣都未必撥到款<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T02:42:50.000Z","msg":"唔一定,高鐵埋左尾,屯門公路擴闊同灣仔嬈道又完晒工,得番港珠澳,三跑同蓮塘,你叫堆工人去邊,夾岩TIMING真係可能搞得成"},{"pid":"06f03baccd2deed0675ed8779f8e33c6f9cf1d17","tid":530581,"uid":35519,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T02:43:19.000Z","msg":"過去有意見提出興建「荃屯鐵路」，由屯門西出發，經掃管笏、深井至荃灣西，疏導屯門區經西鐵綫出市區的交通問題。可是，此走線不能解決早上繁忙時間絕大部份的新界西北居民往九龍和港島的交通問題，因為在這段繁忙時間內，西鐵綫在大欖隧道段已完全飽和，而每一列車在荃灣西站只有數十人下車。<br />\n<br />\n至於屯九鐵路，「實政圓桌」建議的走線是由屯門西經掃管笏/大欖、青龍頭/深井、灣景花園、梨木樹、石籬至美孚。往九龍和港島的乘客可在美孚轉車，大大紓緩西鐵綫「迫爆」問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/605850/xlarge/5aab1b64194ae5f4e88be7c8f497d8e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F605850%2Fxlarge%2F5aab1b64194ae5f4e88be7c8f497d8e0.jpg&h=e6ea125a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7cca6f2b31c03a2a3062854452f11e2c9f7bab1f","tid":530581,"uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T02:46:31.000Z","msg":"首先，屯門至機場條隧道都未起完，而且無預留鐵路隧道，加上又要穿過漂移人工島，大嶼山、同埋青州，預2000億走唔甩"},{"pid":"cd8e175715dfd0a3af6457b6177a338b8c6d46f1","tid":530581,"uid":35519,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3214cb70274e793faba3876d5e409913a3c49b71","tid":530581,"uid":115525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"210ea137164d82edeacad8c0547a7eebc50fca45","tid":530581,"uid":77196,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T02:36:26.000Z","msg":"呢條路個Idea Loop左幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T02:38:30.000Z","msg":"我都想知聽左幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T02:47:54.000Z","msg":"1986年，九廣鐵路公司開始進行1986年香港輕鐵系統擴展研究計劃，在新界西部興建鐵路連接九龍西及新界西，屯荃鐵路的走線因而再次提起，可惜該線段再次被否決"},{"pid":"5137ca72bd068fc69080135e20d743aad54bcb10","tid":530581,"uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"210ea137164d82edeacad8c0547a7eebc50fca45","tid":530581,"uid":77196,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T02:36:26.000Z","msg":"呢條路個Idea Loop左幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T02:48:08.000Z","msg":"西部外走廊同西部走廊鐵路一齊起近三十年 <br />\n屯荃鐵路就算鳩數啦, 港共政府都識敷衍戇柒鳩田北俊細佬同班區議員focus喺九龍-交倚洲過海道路"},{"pid":"e1a65c40fa7b5463824910ab97f12052c842a6bd","tid":530581,"uid":35870,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T02:49:13.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n將d錢放落本地基建，好過dum落去高鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown