桌」建議的走線是由屯門西經掃管笏/大欖、青龍頭/深井、灣景花園、梨木樹、石籬至美孚。往九龍和港島的乘客可在美孚轉車，大大紓緩西鐵綫「迫爆」問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/605850/xlarge/5aab1b64194ae5f4e88be7c8f497d8e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F605850%2Fxlarge%2F5aab1b64194ae5f4e88be7c8f497d8e0.jpg&h=e6ea125a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T02:52:07.000Z","msg":"梨木樹站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然起完我都應該搬走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2d308ae5a680dd088a9ef8e78098c46bb5bdcf","tid":530581,"uid":57005,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"683e90400fdac58ec6268cb855eb1fdeb83d49e9","tid":530581,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"06f03baccd2deed0675ed8779f8e33c6f9cf1d17","tid":530581,"uid":35519,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T02:43:19.000Z","msg":"過去有意見提出興建「荃屯鐵路」，由屯門西出發，經掃管笏、深井至荃灣西，疏導屯門區經西鐵綫出市區的交通問題。可是，此走線不能解決早上繁忙時間絕大部份的新界西北居民往九龍和港島的交通問題，因為在這段繁忙時間內，西鐵綫在大欖隧道段已完全飽和，而每一列車在荃灣西站只有數十人下車。<br />\n<br />\n至於屯九鐵路，「實政圓桌」建議的走線是由屯門西經掃管笏/大欖、青龍頭/深井、灣景花園、梨木樹、石籬至美孚。往九龍和港島的乘客可在美孚轉車，大大紓緩西鐵綫「迫爆」問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/605850/xlarge/5aab1b64194ae5f4e88be7c8f497d8e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F605850%2Fxlarge%2F5aab1b64194ae5f4e88be7c8f497d8e0.jpg&h=e6ea125a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T02:52:07.000Z","msg":"梨木樹站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然起完我都應該搬走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" clas